snippet.title: Numgeon: Trailer
snippet.description:
Numgeon is tiny, retro styled, highly-addictive and fast paced clicker game.

Click your way through the darkest dungeons with your mighty heroes!

Slay the monsters, collect gold and gain new upgrades as you progress. Are your fast fingers ready?


Twitter: @FobTi
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/990640/Numgeon
